      • 序列化字段

        • dlx

          DLX dlx
          DLX instance.

        • solution

          java.util.List<E> solution
          The solution got from DLX.solve. For every tile, the first element is the number of the tile, others are positions.

        • numOfSolution

          int numOfSolution
          The number of possible solutions.

        • board

        • colors

          Control panel.

        • pDisplay

          javax.swing.JPanel pDisplay
          Display panel to show tiles.

        • posMap

          int[] posMap
          Use to map solution from DancingLinks class to actual position. In order to reduce the time complexity to O(1), an array is used.

        • speed

          int speed
          The speed of the single step and single solution. from 1ms to 500ms.
